地產公司承認，因為見到網上短片，決定解僱呢位田女士。<br />\n<br />\n唔知當日令個妹成為Lil Tay呢個角色嘅，係個妹妹自己想咁，定係大人「培育」呢？<br />\n<br />\nbtw把口咁mean啲slang又咁純熟，我幾想學。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Ig: liltay</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:14:29.000Z","msg":"張相個樣邊只9歲？19我都信"},{"pid":"9c8d219b65a1bd663a0a815ee1b23bc9d06aec7d","tid":661171,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"165fa855674d0b94f2bdf00246f3daaa98de5e3b","tid":661171,"uid":70201,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d0a5730d75c1c60bf52dc669dc3b2271c0db809","tid":661171,"uid":37005,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"75306aec0d5d03e7d691fb22fd0262446c5dba25","tid":661171,"uid":70201,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T12:23:44.000Z","msg":"據聞啲車同豪宅純粹係佢阿媽用agent身份book俾個女拍片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣有咩謂呢其實。。。自欺欺人"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"不如問佢阿媽俾個女咁樣有咩謂先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:15:23.000Z","msg":"咪就係想知個阿媽咁做有咩謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你以為我問你?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02ecc5d8e47d1af635e95c8b219661af63c7614","tid":661171,"uid":70201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c8d219b65a1bd663a0a815ee1b23bc9d06aec7d","tid":661171,"uid":37005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"165fa855674d0b94f2bdf00246f3daaa98de5e3b","tid":661171,"uid":70201,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"4d0a5730d75c1c60bf52dc669dc3b2271c0db809","tid":661171,"uid":37005,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-11T13:09:01.000Z","msg":"吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁樣有